# 🎂 Build a Premium Birthday Surprise Website

Create a modern, premium-quality, fully responsive single-page birthday surprise website dedicated to **"Abii Akka"**. The website should feel emotional, elegant, and interactive, using smooth animations, beautiful typography, and a soft pink, purple, and gold color theme. The design should be mobile-friendly and desktop-friendly.

## General Requirements

* Single-page responsive website
* HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Clean, modular code
* Smooth scrolling
* Premium UI/UX
* Fast loading
* Beautiful entrance animations
* No login or backend required

